body: Replaces #29 License downloaded from ~https://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0.en.html~ https://raw.githubusercontent.com/IQAndreas/markdown-licenses/master/gnu-agpl-v3.0.md Using the license from IQAndreas' repo as it's prettier, has the same information, and uses semantically correct markup. --- This change isâ€‚[](https://reviewable.io/reviews/toktok/website/38)
